name: KM-QRS
body:
### Welcome to KeyMic's Quote Rating System
You've seen it all over the web. System where you can post content and that content gets some form of like/dislike reaction.

### Support or Contact
Having trouble with KM-QRS? Contact me or create a [github issue](https://github.com/keymic/km-qrs/issues/new).
